{"tid":1018994,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［PHY高手入］點解溫度會影響太陽能電池既電壓同電流？","createTime":"2019-02-12T15:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T17:35:10.000Z","uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dcc9018c3374b3213d44648c03cd3582caf0f7fe","tid":1018994,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"溫度較高時，current上升，voltage下降<br />\n溫度較低時，current下降，voltage上升<br />\n<br />\n上網搵過資料，<br />\n當溫度較高時，有較多electrons獲得足夠既energy跳過band gap，所以current上升，呢部份都明（假設我無理解錯）<br />\n<br />\n但唔太明點解會影響埋voltage （唔好答V=IR，因為呢個case V同I唔係成正比）<br />\n<br />\n求PHY高手指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9095e29a09362a0e493b5892951a9846e7d34b","tid":1018994,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c042747804ecd292a113d74204b38042357e5f20","tid":1018994,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb51dad69bb8225443d24d151253702844a9ac4d","tid":1018994,"uid":22302,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"鳩估<br />\n因為除左多左electron跳過到band gap之外，每粒過到band gap既electron都多左energy，所以voltage都高左"},{"pid":"23c1389c96f284a824c49f2e426dcf68c5e86f13","tid":1018994,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"利申：physics入面我讀得最差就係electronics<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6459adf8910c7f88418a618cbb589bbb9d14172c","tid":1018994,"uid":164950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"Internal resistance 隨溫度上升而上升，terminal voltage 會跟I乘以R 咁跌得多啲"},{"pid":"331487419b8e1a66ee57b7c53e5cfa3062c8feaf","tid":1018994,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6459adf8910c7f88418a618cbb589bbb9d14172c","tid":1018994,"uid":164950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"Internal resistance 隨溫度上升而上升，terminal voltage 會跟I乘以R 咁跌得多啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"但semiconductor既resistance隨溫度上升而下降喎<br />\nSor上面講漏左，solar cell係用silicon作為材料"},{"pid":"28c86348c577150b89a2782f9183cccbaa4ae8cb","tid":1018994,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb51dad69bb8225443d24d151253702844a9ac4d","tid":1018994,"uid":22302,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"鳩估<br />\n因為除左多左electron跳過到band gap之外，每粒過到band gap既electron都多左energy，所以voltage都高左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"但而家個情況係用semiconductor做既solar cell，temperature increase時，current increase and voltage decrease，個voltage係低左"},{"pid":"fa5daba7a8949bc17cb9943cb0a6c4d1a603a9d6","tid":1018994,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pveducation.org/pvcdrom/solar-cell-operation/effect-of-temperature\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pveducation.org%2Fpvcdrom%2Fsolar-cell-operation%2Feffect-of-temperature&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=cc47ab49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pveducation.org/pvcdrom/solar-cell-operation/effect-of-temperature</a><br />\n利申: 唔識"},{"pid":"503c7a9519c998b937a2483ce7d7f5661633d9f6","tid":1018994,"uid":232594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:12:30.000Z","msg":"冇得咁比的，你要比較current就要same voltage下先比較到，你要講voltage就要same current下先比較到<br />\n<br />\n下面呢張圖係google番黎，講緊半導體(即太陽能電池) 係唔同溫度下current同voltage關係，你只可以話同一current下，溫度愈高voltage愈低，無得同時講兩樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/emedia-stash/0f26e8c7-85d3-463b-a004-b10a9c36749d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Femedia-stash%2F0f26e8c7-85d3-463b-a004-b10a9c36749d.jpg&h=990cb6fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.edntaiwan.com/news/article/20170915TA01-semiconductor-temperature\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edntaiwan.com%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170915TA01-semiconductor-temperature&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=8f430b2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edntaiwan.com/news/article/20170915TA01-semiconductor-temperature</a>"},{"pid":"04a3018b2a22e26c6d15d4618cd47935c4fbecde","tid":1018994,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"咁都要問"},{"pid":"4ed40df6b787a9c276411ffab469fd9a4f25b614","tid":1018994,"uid":37719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"純9up:<br />\n有條式好似係v=一堆野跟住ln(np/ni^2)咁上下<br />\n溫度高左&gt;ni大左&gt;v趺"},{"pid":"6e28695b0aea919b229552b563c5ab314de5b99b","tid":1018994,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"331487419b8e1a66ee57b7c53e5cfa3062c8feaf","tid":1018994,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6459adf8910c7f88418a618cbb589bbb9d14172c","tid":1018994,"uid":164950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"Internal resistance 隨溫度上升而上升，terminal voltage 會跟I乘以R 咁跌得多啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"但semiconductor既resistance隨溫度上升而下降喎<br />\nSor上面講漏左，solar cell係用silicon作為材料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"Sor睇錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d78946f50374c7f34f6a3fb40176b425bf1892","tid":1018994,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:42:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9f4c760ce33f2d510fed3f3e3d6ab2b039ae40e","tid":1018994,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ed40df6b787a9c276411ffab469fd9a4f25b614","