voltage就要same current下先比較到<br />\n<br />\n下面呢張圖係google番黎，講緊半導體(即太陽能電池) 係唔同溫度下current同voltage關係，你只可以話同一current下，溫度愈高voltage愈低，無得同時講兩樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/emedia-stash/0f26e8c7-85d3-463b-a004-b10a9c36749d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Femedia-stash%2F0f26e8c7-85d3-463b-a004-b10a9c36749d.jpg&h=990cb6fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.edntaiwan.com/news/article/20170915TA01-semiconductor-temperature\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edntaiwan.com%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170915TA01-semiconductor-temperature&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=8f430b2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edntaiwan.com/news/article/20170915TA01-semiconductor-temperature</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:53:54.000Z","msg":"Thx bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但上網睇，都有唔少lab既結果係做緊difference temperature, current同voltage都會同時改變，就係呢個位諗唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb89cee9c57edc7d06bab6828254db337dd1392b","tid":1018994,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ed40df6b787a9c276411ffab469fd9a4f25b614","tid":1018994,"uid":37719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"純9up:<br />\n有條式好似係v=一堆野跟住ln(np/ni^2)咁上下<br />\n溫度高左&gt;ni大左&gt;v趺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:57:30.000Z","msg":"呢個似係喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但條式都只係反映左溫度/ni同V既關係，想貪心少少知埋條式背後既意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw，都明唔係所有關係都一定可以解釋，<br />\n就好似最簡單既F=ma，要睇三者關係好容易，但要我解釋點解F同m會有咁既關係，我都解唔到（可能我廢）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5817b24f6705353b66a2fedbe9314d8f7d98c0c7","tid":1018994,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:02:37.000Z","msg":"呢個位關唔關quantum事？<br />\n即係過到band gap的electron本身excited去一個更高的energy level，所以voltage 更高 (J/C 的定義)"},{"pid":"b1f18534fc0a96bcefd2f7f86d7c06421d626479","tid":1018994,"uid":64278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cb059e82afbb746830bb4fb7555b8d073d6e2a7","tid":1018994,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa5daba7a8949bc17cb9943cb0a6c4d1a603a9d6","tid":1018994,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pveducation.org/pvcdrom/solar-cell-operation/effect-of-temperature\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pveducation.org%2Fpvcdrom%2Fsolar-cell-operation%2Feffect-of-temperature&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=cc47ab49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pveducation.org/pvcdrom/solar-cell-operation/effect-of-temperature</a><br />\n利申: 唔識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:52:31.000Z","msg":"睇過但都係唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:35:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pveducation.org/pvcdrom/solar-cell-operation/iv-curve\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pveducation.org%2Fpvcdrom%2Fsolar-cell-operation%2Fiv-curve&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=e5ebd70c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pveducation.org/pvcdrom/solar-cell-operation/iv-curve</a><br />\n<br />\nYou need this too. <br />\n<br />\nI_0 係reverse biased current without light"}]}